 Optimising database (Using Set, arithmetic, logical and special operators) 
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1)Display customer_id,CITY  who lives 'EKM' and 'TVM'(using set operation)

mysql> SELECT * FROM CUSTOMER;
